HEADWORD: Sea pork
<hw>Sea" pork`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An American
compound ascidian (<spn>Amoroecium stellatum</spn>) which forms large
whitish masses resembling salt pork.</def>⟦br⟧
